e seedy looking characters that hung around the hotel-I noticed this too and not sure if they were guests, or just locals. Lots of foreigners stay here since it's cheaper. Like I said, the rooms are great size with a sofa and a table, but they have those noisy old A/C units in them. If all you want is a clean place to stay that's really affordable, this may do the trick but do not expect anything fancy.	
